                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Delgado</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Consulate of the United States,<lb/>Matanzas</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1896-09-11">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 11, 1896</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Oscar Cespedes American citizen. Confined castle September 6. Afterwards removed
                    to jail infirmary, Reported very ill. Have informed Consul Lee.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Delgado.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
